tral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">(97% post-consumer metals)</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Black Wire Binding</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Bronze Wire</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Bronze Wire Binding</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Pewter Wire</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Pewter Wire Binding</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">White Wire Binding</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Pen Imprint</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Minimum of 250 pieces\r\nPen Imprint area is .25&quot; x 2.25&quot;.  \r\nYour choice of Matte Gold or Silver, Black or White ink.\r\nPen imprinting can add 3 days to production time.\r\nPrice is based on pen purchased with a journal</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Black Ink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Matte Gold Ink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Matte Silver Ink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">White Ink</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Foil Setup &amp; Color Choice</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Colors shown are approximate and used as reference only.\r\nRun Fees - The 1st Color Foil or Blind Deboss (depending on the product) imprint run fee is included in the cost of the book.  Each additional color, deboss &amp;/or location imprint will experience a run fee of $0.48(G) per book plus the setup die fee.\r\nThe foil colors have limited application on poly cover material. Those colors marked as &quot;POLY on the foil color chart have been proven to work well on Poly materials. Metallic foils which include gloss black are 100% opaque. Pigmented foils may change in opacity depending on the lightness or darkness of the cover material chosen (our standard pigment foils are very opaque). The following foil chart has been designed with foils that are proven to stamp well on our cover materials. These standard foils are always in stock, any other selection may require additional production time.\r\nPMS matching is not available with foils however we can attempt to come close to your color needs.  Some limitations and additional production time may apply.  Please consult with the factory for custom requests.</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Satin Silver</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Silver Satin Metallic Foil</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Green #6</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Green #6 Metallic Foil</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Orange</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Orange Gloss Foil</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Pink</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Pink Gloss Foil</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Satin Teal Metallic</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Teal Satin Metallic Foil</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Yellow</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Yellow Gloss Foil</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Blue #1</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Blue #1 Matte Foil</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Blue #2</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Blue #2 Matte Foil</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Blue #3</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Blue #3 Matte Foil</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Blue #4</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Blue #4 Gloss Foil</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-